{"tid":2514220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支聯會聲援學生  譴責校方割席  洗國殤之柱 抗港大打壓","createTime":"2021-05-03T06:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T06:21:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b841e00f5397a58a7af20a14a4ee351bd7c7260c","tid":2514220,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T06:21:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/GGAYNDTDEZFWTP7LOSWDDJPQ7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FGGAYNDTDEZFWTP7LOSWDDJPQ7Q%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=eef6cfa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FGGAYNDTDEZFWTP7LOSWDDJPQ7Q%2F&h=4e30c24a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/GGAYNDTDEZFWTP7LOSWDDJPQ7Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n支聯會聲援學生  譴責校方割席 <br />\n洗國殤之柱 抗港大打壓<br />\n<br />\n【風雨不改】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港大學校方日前表示將收回學生會大樓等設施管理權，令人關注由學生會管理、悼念六四死難者的「國殤之柱」能否繼續安放於港大，支聯會昨日一如既往到港大洗刷國殤之柱，晚上燃點燭光悼念六四及默哀。支聯會副主席鄒幸彤表示，事前未收過校方聯絡，至今不知校方會如何處置國殤之柱，但強調校方不應連一支紀念歷史、記錄真相的柱也不能容納。<br />\n<br />\n今年是六四32周年，亦是五四運動102周年，支聯會昨日到港大洗刷國殤之柱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fdwosSSY4VeFb7MVGjEIL1fbcb4=/510x339/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AYJ7MOTMIZHWFBR4F7VS6I3C6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfdwosSSY4VeFb7MVGjEIL1fbcb4%3D%2F510x339%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAYJ7MOTMIZHWFBR4F7VS6I3C6Y.jpg&h=be1eb315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■支聯會成員昨按傳統洗刷國殤之柱，點起燭光悼念六四死者。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保安拍攝 登記傳媒資料<br />\n<br />\n校方昨日雖然未有阻止支聯會活動，但有加強保安，鄰近國殤之柱有超過10名保安人員駐守，有保安人員登記在場記者資料，並拍攝整個活動過程。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會副主席何俊仁、鄒幸彤等人身穿印有「為自由 共命運 同抗爭」字句的衣服，並叫喊「平反八九民運」、「結束一黨專政」等口號，稱會堅持爭取民主。晚上6時20分他們燃點燭光及默哀一分鐘悼念死者。<br />\n<br />\n鄒幸彤接受訪問時表示，支聯會從未有收過港大就洗刷國殤之柱一事的聯絡，他們至今也不知校方將會如何處置國殤之柱，故此難以估計下年的洗刷國殤之柱活動能否舉行。但她強調，校方不應該「連一支紀念歷史、記錄真相嘅柱都容納唔到」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到日前港大校方宣佈與學生會割席事件，鄒幸彤形容事件荒謬，譴責港大之餘，認為學校有責任保護學生；學生會是民主運動的忠堅分子，支聯會一定會與受打壓學生「企埋一齊」，促請校方收回割席決定。<br />\n<br />\n至於香港日後是否「連燭光都有罪」、支聯會能否再辦六四燭光集會等，鄒幸彤指「就算政權定義燭光有罪，我哋都會繼續支持」，促請港人不忘六四，與抗爭者繼續同行。<br />\n<br />\n何俊仁表示，支聯會努力推動民主自由，亦藉洗刷國殤之柱懷念已故前主席司徒華，並指國殤之柱有20年歷史，富有象徵意義，不能分割，促請校方尊重自由及歷史。支聯會正計劃本月16日舉行「毋忘六四」長跑，並正就六四集會申請不反對通知，強調定必堅持在維園舉行燭光集會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f9LTHXjvGppKi42UkIXE9Y82Smc=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BSNYXAYG5BH57EY2W7YW3CLUJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff9LTHXjvGppKi42UkIXE9Y82Smc%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBSNYXAYG5BH57EY2W7YW3CLUJU.jpg&h=139d8734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■支聯會昨一如既往洗刷柱身，毋忘歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c0PoxQ7Azf3eQTzK5vMlI9MvUG8=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SY4YYWK7WZHCTM4DWLABNVVGGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fc0PoxQ7Azf3eQTzK5vMlI9MvUG8%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSY4YYWK7WZHCTM4DWLABNVVGGY.jpg&h=39580780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■由學生會管理的國殤之柱未知能否繼續安放於港大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SpDuD9u0lcWBzVhL1beIw3texyQ=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J6DNTOW6JBCJ7MNKQF6EWFFBV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSpDuD9u0lcWBzVhL1beIw3texyQ%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ6DNTOW6JBCJ7MNKQF6EWFFBV4.jpg&h=5f75fe78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■保安人員在遠距離駐守監視。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dgLsIZ5yo_FbkrlNTl48VK6ia3M=/510x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SXSXN5V43JE4LI3OLXRIPKS33I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdgLsIZ5yo_FbkrlNTl48VK6ia3M%3D%2F510x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSXSXN5V43JE4LI3OLXRIPKS33I.jpg&h=73040430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港大保安人員登記記者資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n5JeE-f0jd3ICRdNGi_jZkB3OJA=/510x556/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SL72BVCGEZFOZASPE7ZCAEMHLI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn5JeE-f0jd3ICRdNGi_jZkB3OJA%3D%2F510x556%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSL72BVCGEZFOZASPE7ZCAEMHLI.jpg&h=77385034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■何俊仁（左）及鄒幸彤手持燭光悼念六四死者。"}]}